Steps to be able to run the framework:

1. Install python 3 (https://www.python.org/downloads/). Remember to add python path to the system's environment variables.

2. Install pandas package for python through the command window: pip3 install pandas

3. Install PyQt5 package for python through the command window: pip3 install PyQt5

4. Download the .zip folder (at https://github.com/alarca94/fakenews-annotator) or clone the github repository through the command window with: git clone https://github.com/alarca94/fakenews-annotator.git

5. Run from the console window (located at the annotator directory that was just downloaded/cloned): python3 gui.py